    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package on the basis of the Monte Carlo UQ results and the supplemental experimental comparison incorporated after initial signing. The post-signing evidence update was noted in the record but the package was not re-signed, introducing a consistency gap (W-CON-03). All seven assessed credibility factors show achieved levels below required levels; six factors remain as epistemic gaps at MRL 5. Acceptance is conditional and subject to re-evaluation upon re-signing.",
